me function cannot be algebraic.\nAlso we calculate the local monodromy groups, describing the ramification of\nvolume functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 20:05:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
