sive experiments on CIFAR-10, CIFAR-100, and\nMini-Imagenet datasets, our proposed method is shown to achieve superior\nperformance against various baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 05:29:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2023 10:11:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-16"}
