 motion and adjusting\nthe patient setup for abdominal SBRT. CBCT can be used for motion modeling,\npotentially eliminating the need for additional fluoroscopic pair acquisition\nand thus reducing the imaging dose to the patient and the total treatment time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 07:10:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
