ons, since the\ntotal energy densities at the hydrodynamization times fall inside and outside\nthe conformal window for the two sectors respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 10:55:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-11"}
