ents explaining experimental recovery;\n(3) explain the combined impact of interactions between wettability /\nsaturation functions, viscosities and other input on early- and late time\nrecovery behavior.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 20:50:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-15"}
